# AI coding agents and tools
brew "sst/tap/opencode" # This is a OSS Code Agent for the terminal. [OpenCode](https://github.com/sst/opencode)
brew "gemini-cli" # Google's AI coding agent for the terminal. [Gemini CLI](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli)
brew "kimi-cli" # Moonshot AI's coding agent for the terminal. [Kimi CLI](https://github.com/MoonshotAI/kimi-cli)
